Uploading multiple files in Rails without Flash can be difficult. This site is an example of how to submit a form to an iframe and respond to it's parent with a response.

This project uses a few plugins, including attachment_fu, jRails, and responds_to_parent. It will not degrade gracefully, as it relies heavily on JS, but who cares.

Check out the blog post about it at http://prowestech.com/posts